Class Date

  • java.lang.Object
    • Date

  • public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
    Date class responsible for holding date of when members join. Holds the month, day, and year. Provides functionality to validate the date, compare if two dates are the same, and print date as string.
    Author:
    Tin Fung, Rizwan Chowdhury
